        <graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="12859_2020_3894_Figa_HTML" id="MO6"/>
        <p id="Par55">The topic of document ranking functions is addressed later in this section. For the sake of completeness, we note that we use the same ranking function r (with the same free parameters) within RM3 and in the final search with the expanded query. We sacrifice the possibility of fully parameterising the RM3 runs for the overall simplicity of the system.</p>
